               <msContents defective="false">
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1" defective="false">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the protagonist; names of the previous donors (in most cases erased and replaced with that of other names in black ink); elements of the punctuation signs and of the text dividers; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
&#xD;
Several groups of lines on the incipit page of Text I (alternating with black lines); two initial lines in the incipit of sections (homilies) and subsections (miracles and commemorative notices); the first word in the incipit of subsections (hymns), i.e. sälam "salutation".</rubric>
