            <listPerson default="false">
               <person instant="false"><!--donor-->
                  <persName corresp="PRS0000" instant="false" full="yes">According to Additio 1, Gäbrä Ṣadǝq donated the Ms. to the church of Dändära Mikaʾel. His name and the name of his wife, ʾAmätä Mikaʾel, were written in supplication formulas over the (sometimes erased) names of the original donors, probably in the same hand that wrote Additio 1. The names of the original donors can be deciphered as Wäldä Mikaʾel and Wälättä Gärima (s. fols. 19ra, 28vb, 32va); the name of Täsfa ʾIyäsus is written on fol. 57ra.</persName>
